title: Good Omens Theme Song... But With Lyrics | Prime Video
author: Amazon Prime Video UK
comment: Sorry but "ineffable... friends" is the funniest dodged lyric ever

We all thought she was going to say ineffable husbands, didn't we? 
Also, I LOVE THE FACT THAT AMAZON IS STILL IN FANBOY MODE WITH THE SHOW
"Ineffable friends" what a lie, they're married
Aside from the “friends” this video is perfect.
this most certainly gets a “wahoo!” from me
description:
We love what the legions of Good Omens fans around the world are making. Mega-fan Emma Blackery has put some (unofficial) lyrics of her own to David Arnold's iconic theme song - and we love it!
